<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">
It is distributed in Europe, Turkey, Caucasus and Russia to Central Asia (
<bibRefCitation author="Wojas, T." journalOrPublisher="Wiadomosci Entomologiczne" pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" refId="B6007957" refString="Catalog World Spider World Spider Catalog. Version 21.5 http://wsc.nmbe.ch 2020-03-15T00:00:00+02:00" year="2011">World Spider Catalog 2020</bibRefCitation>
). It can be found in mainland Italy (
<bibRefCitation author="Pantini, Paolo" journalOrPublisher="Fragmenta Entomologica" pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" pagination="127 - 152" refId="B6007828" refString="Pantini, Paolo, Isaia, Marco, 2019. Araneae.it: the online Catalog of Italian spiders, with addenda on other Arachnid Orders occurring in Italy (Arachnida: Araneae, Opiliones, Palpigradi, Pseudoscorpionida, Scorpiones, Solifugae). Fragmenta Entomologica 51 (2): 127 - 152" title="Araneae. it: the online Catalog of Italian spiders, with addenda on other Arachnid Orders occurring in Italy (Arachnida: Araneae, Opiliones, Palpigradi, Pseudoscorpionida, Scorpiones, Solifugae)" volume="51" year="2019">Pantini and Isaia 2019</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">
Lives in humid and shady habitats: in forests, in peat bogs or on the soil of the riparian zone (
<bibRefCitation author="Bazelet, Corinna S." journalOrPublisher="Ecological Indicators" pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" pagination="1259 - 1269" refId="B5894366" refString="Bazelet, Corinna S., Samways, Michael J., 2011. Identifying grasshopper bioindicators for habitat quality assessment of ecological networks. Ecological Indicators 11 (5): 1259 - 1269" title="Identifying grasshopper bioindicators for habitat quality assessment of ecological networks" volume="11" year="2011">Bazelet and Samways 2011</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Roberts, M. J." journalOrPublisher="Collins Field Guide. Harper Collins Publishers" pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" refId="B6007965" refString="Roberts, M. J., 1995. Spiders of Britain &amp; Northern Europe. Collins Field Guide. Harper Collins Publishers" title="Spiders of Britain &amp; Northern Europe" year="1995">Roberts 1995</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
